Working Title: DEBUF: Destroying Evil Baddie Universally Forever
Concept Statement: Using incremental style benefits from a elder god, RPG your way through a set amount of randomly assorted bosses and areas until you can defeat the BBEG, utilising debuffs, specific vulnerabilities and out of dungeon effects to get the upperhand.
Genres: RPG, Rougelite, Incremental
Target Audience: RPG Intermediates/Veterans 30-45 Softly Leaning Male ESRB Mature (17+)
Unique Selling Points: Debuffing led design with a strong meta progression elements, and a loadout structure. Eldritch horror where you are alongside the horror not wholy or mostly pit against it.

Player Experience and Game POV: The player is the first adventurer to non violently and not offend the elder god "pixie" character in 10000 years. A genteel homely homebase area with a gothic torture dungeon aesthetic as you travel the backside of the BBEG's castle.
